{"tid":2312443,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"武俠小說的反英雄（antihero）推介？","createTime":"2020-12-05T03:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T16:19:57.000Z","uid":139500,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"deb3ff5602107328cfa02814b3f4cef2b4116a69","tid":2312443,"uid":139500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T03:14:52.000Z","msg":"根據維基：<br />\n反英雄是文學、電影、戲劇作品中，形象接近反派角色或有缺點的普通人，但同時具有英雄氣質或做出英雄行為的角色。反英雄可以是主角或重要的配角。<br />\n<br />\n我自己對反英雄的定義：<br />\n反英雄心中有一套個人的原則，係佢地心目中，呢套原則凌駕一切的法律條文， 或者社會的道德規範。佢地有唔少的英雄行為，可惜只會有少數人知道，或者會比社會大眾曲解成包裝技巧。<br />\n<br />\n我最鐘意的反英雄：李尋歡<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩反英雄推介？"},{"pid":"89def72b3920b32f9b03c03ae17f805f5d6fb4a1","tid":2312443,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:08:18.000Z","msg":"唔係武俠小說<br />\nFate zero 既Kiritsugu Emiya 算唔算？"},{"pid":"989ffb85a01bd656beabe4b94ee9fd834e73da94","tid":2312443,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"古龍大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實李尋歡都唔太算 根本就聖人黎 傅紅雪應該似D"},{"pid":"b51caa59b6d66224a43fb9c5aca75ce2683d758b","tid":2312443,"uid":213656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"流星蝴蝶劍算唔算？"},{"pid":"69207788a62751dc0a60a1dd8b13fad0a1d35730","tid":2312443,"uid":4874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"韋小寶？"},{"pid":"50b68f832389e59d751cea1d88ec975b6854b4e9","tid":2312443,"uid":139500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89def72b3920b32f9b03c03ae17f805f5d6fb4a1","tid":2312443,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:08:18.000Z","msg":"唔係武俠小說<br />\nFate zero 既Kiritsugu Emiya 算唔算？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"睇過動畫，呢排想睇書多D"},{"pid":"f3462fa841e6c42277d1349f248c69ade8807ea2","tid":2312443,"uid":139500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98